data.description: GORGEOUS REMODEL in the very popular Buckner Terrace! This charmer features a light & bright floor plan with beautiful flooring, new windows, new kitchen, updated baths, new light fixtures, fresh paint, plus a fresh elevation & new landscaping. Kitchen has ample counter & cabinet space, granite counters, SS appliances. Living area has WBFP with cedar mantle, built-ins, French doors to backyard. Nice sized dedicated dining area off kitchen. Master has private bath with barn door. Two additional bedrooms & another bath. Baths have modern tile & new fixtures. New privacy fence added! AMAZING curb appeal+move in ready! Easy commute to downtown; close to White Rock Lake, Dallas Arboretum, Casa Linda Shopping Center.
